CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 20, 1957, page A10, reads: "Likes to Cook - Mrs. Blana Williams of Linron St. recently celebrated her 87th birthday. She came to Pittsburgh from Charlotte, Va., 67 years ago. She has a great sense of humor and loves to cook. - Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of eight women, including elderly Blana Williams wearing checkered dress, and man, gathered around table, with round cake for 87th birthday, in domestic interior with floral wallpaper, and fireplace with cat figurine on mantle
